<paragraph id="A04136BFFF876018FBADFEF06354920B" blockId="27.[136,1452,158,581]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
The name 
<taxonomicName id="67FE4D3CFF876018FA2DFEF167FB91DF" box="[317,501,374,401]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ptarmicoides">
<emphasis id="928AEAADFF876018FA2DFEF167FB91DF" box="[317,501,374,401]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">C. ptarmicoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation id="C46F4B4EFF876018F9F1FEF065AE91DE" author="Halacsy, E. von" box="[737,928,374,401]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" refId="ref114663" refString="Halacsy, E. von (1902 b) Conspectus florae graecae Vol. 2 (2). G. Engelmann, Lipsiae [Leipzig], 356 pp." type="book" year="1902">Halácsy (1902b)</bibRefCitation>
only in the index of his 
<emphasis id="928AEAADFF876018FFC2FEF166E691FA" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Conspectus Florae Graecae</emphasis>
2, most probably with the intention to replace the epithet 
<emphasis id="928AEAADFF876018F86BFE1D65D191FB" box="[891,991,411,436]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">epirotica</emphasis>
, as on the indicated page he only gave a new combination of 
<taxonomicName id="67FE4D3CFF876018FA7CFE3964BF9197" authority="Bald." authorityName="Bald." box="[364,689,446,473]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="deusta" variety="epirotica">
<emphasis id="928AEAADFF876018FA7CFE3967DB9197" box="[364,469,446,473]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">C. deusta</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="928AEAADFF876018F91BFE3964619197" box="[523,623,447,472]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">epirotica</emphasis>
Bald.
</taxonomicName>
for 
<taxonomicName id="67FE4D3CFF876018F9CDFE3962B59197" authority="(Bald.) Halacsy. Hayek (1931)" authorityName="Halacsy. Hayek" authorityYear="1931" baseAuthorityName="Bald." box="[733,1211,446,473]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="epirotica">
<emphasis id="928AEAADFF876018F9CDFE39656F9197" box="[733,865,447,473]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">C. epirotica</emphasis>
(Bald.) Halácsy. 
<bibRefCitation id="C46F4B4EFF876018FF32FE3862B59197" author="Hayek, A." box="[1058,1211,446,472]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" pagination="769 - 960" refId="ref116316" refString="Hayek, A. (1931) Prodromus florae peninsulae balcanicae. Repertorium specierum novarum regni vegetabilis. Beiheft 30 2 (Lief. 6): 769 - 960." type="journal article" year="1931">Hayek (1931)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
took 
<taxonomicName id="67FE4D3CFF876018FFE9FE39675891B3" authority="Halacsy ex Hayek" authorityName="Hayek" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ptarmicifolia">
<emphasis id="928AEAADFF876018FFE9FE3963A59197" box="[1273,1451,446,473]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">C. ptarmicifolia</emphasis>
Halácsy ex Hayek
</taxonomicName>
(as 
<emphasis id="928AEAADFF876018FA98FE64642391B3" box="[392,557,482,508]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">ptarmicaefolia</emphasis>
) as replacement name. According to the decision of the special Committee for 
<taxonomicName id="67FE4D3CFF876018FB98FD80673C926F" box="[136,306,518,544]" class="Spermatophyta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="class">Spermatophyta</taxonomicName>
