</taxonomicName>
are to be treated as homonyms (
<bibRefCitation id="C46F4B4EFF876018FFE3FD8063AD926F" author="Brummitt, R. K." box="[1267,1443,518,544]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" pagination="559 - 568" refId="ref109513" refString="Brummitt, R. K. (2001) Report of the Committee for Spermatophyta: 51. Taxon 50 (2): 559 - 568. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 1223903" type="journal article" year="2001">Brummitt 2001</bibRefCitation>
) and thus 
<taxonomicName id="67FE4D3CFF876018FBFDFDAD647D920B" authority="Halacsy ex Hayek" authorityName="Hayek" box="[237,627,554,581]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ptarmicifolia">
